    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3>find navigation.html in /source/_includes and replace original code with new code</h3>

<p>&#8220;` html
&hellip;
<form action="https://www.google.com/search" method="get">
  <fieldset role="search"></p>

<!-- original code  -->


<!--     <input type="hidden" name="q" value="site:andystu.github.io" /> &#8211;>


<!-- //original code  -->




<!-- new code -->


<pre><code>&lt;input type="hidden" name="sitesearch" value="andystu.github.io" /&gt;
</code></pre>

<!-- //new code -->


<pre><code>&lt;input class="search" type="text" name="q" results="0" placeholder="Search"/&gt;
</code></pre>

<p>  </fieldset>
</form>
&hellip;
&#8220;`</p>

<p>done.</p>

<p>reference
<a href="http://kaspars.net/blog/wordpress/how-to-add-google-site-search">http://kaspars.net/blog/wordpress/how-to-add-google-site-search</a></p>
